The second annual edition of the Spotify Secret Genius Awards held at the Ace Theater in Los Angeles. This year’s awards show was hosted by Ne-Yo. LOS ANGELES, CA – NOVEMBER 16: A view of the atmosphere at Spotify’s Secret Genius Awards hosted by NE-YO at The Theatre at Ace Hotel on November 16, 2018 in Los Angeles, California. Charley Gallay/Getty Images for Spotify/AFP The awards saw awards go to Murda Beatz “Producer of the Year” (Nice for what, Motorsport), Ali Tamposi “Songwriter of the Year” (Havan, Wolves) and Quincy Jones who received the Secret Genius: Legendary Genius Honour. Below are some of the celebrities who attended the event: